American Pension Investors Trust - Yorktown Multi-Asset Income Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 25, 2017 2:03 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of American Pension Investors Trust - Yorktown Multi-Asset Income Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
American Pension Investors Trust - Yorktown Multi-Asset Income Fund is an open ended balanced mutual fund launched and managed by Yorktown Management and Research Co Inc. The fund invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It invests directly and through other funds to create its portfolio. For its equity portion, the fund invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in stocks of companies across all market capitalizations. For its fixed income portion, the fund seeks to invest in debt securities, including U.S. Government securities, corporate bonds and structured notes. It invests in fixed income securities across all maturiti...
American Pension Investors Trust - Yorktown Multi-Asset Income Fund is an open ended balanced mutual fund launched and managed by Yorktown Management and Research Co Inc. The fund invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It invests directly and through other funds to create its portfolio. For its equity portion, the fund invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in stocks of companies across all market capitalizations. For its fixed income portion, the fund seeks to invest in debt securities, including U.S. Government securities, corporate bonds and structured notes. It invests in fixed income securities across all maturities. The fund focuses on factors such as the underlying Funds’ past performance and their investment objectives and policies, the size and cost structure, the investment style, reputation and quality of their investment advisers to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the Dow Jones Conservative Relative Risk Index. The fund was formerly known as American Pension Investors Trust - API Multi-Asset Income Fund. American Pension Investors Trust - Yorktown Multi-Asset Income Fund was formed on July 2, 1997 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


