	API Short Term Bond Fund



	Important Voting Information Inside


	 


















	TABLE OF CONTENTS




	  



	 



	 











	Notice of Special Meeting of Shareholders



	  

















	Important Information to Help You Understand the Proposals



	  



















	Proxy Statement



	  

















	Proposal 1:     To approve changing the Funds Principal
	Investment Objective.



	  

















	Proposal 2:     To transact any other business, not currently
	contemplated, that may properly come before the special meeting of shareholders or any adjournment thereof in the discretion of the proxies or their substitutes.



	  

















